videos.description: Devonte' Graham sets up both Udoka Azubuike and Lagerald Vick with alley-opps early in the first half for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Kansas off to good start with a pair of alley-oops

videos.description: Devonte' Graham shows off some nice handles to create space and knock down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham drains step-back 3-pointer

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk throws it up to Lagerald Vick who dunks home the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Kansas' Vick jams down the lob pass

videos.description: Remy Martin helps force the steal and takes it the other way for the layup.
videos.headline: Arizona State steal leads to Martin layup

videos.description: Shannon Evans II gets the steal and finds Tra Holder in the corner who makes the 3-pointer for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Arizona State turns steal into Holder 3-pointer

videos.description: Shannon Evans II passes to Romello White who makes the shot plus the foul.
videos.headline: Arizona State's White makes and-1 layup

videos.description: Remy Martin picks Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk pocket and goes all the way to make the basket.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Martin gets the steal and layup

videos.description: Devonte' Graham throws the lob and Lagerald Vick makes the great play in the air to dunk it home.
videos.headline: Kansas' Vick rises up to jam home the lob

videos.description: Devonte' Graham turns it over, Remy Martin gets the steal and goes the distance to score for Arizona State.
videos.headline: Martin gets loose ball and scores layup

videos.description: Remy Martin talks with Bill Walton and Roxy Bernstein about his 21-point performance, helping his team pick up a huge road upset at Allen Fieldhouse for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Martin's big game leads Arizona St. to win at No. 2 Kansas
